21
00:01:39,940 --> 00:01:42,620

22
00:01:42,620 --> 00:01:48,471

23
00:01:49,220 --> 00:01:52,020

24
00:02:02,580 --> 00:02:04,280
So?

25
00:02:04,860 --> 00:02:06,340
Baili Dongjun did not take that path.

26
00:02:06,340 --> 00:02:09,120
What? No way!

27
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:12,280
- I told Young Lady— 
 - Young Lady told him to not take that path then.

28
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:14,100
Shut up!

29
00:02:14,100 --> 00:02:16,260
Young Lady...

30
00:02:16,260 --> 00:02:18,900
With Young Lady's status,

31
00:02:19,900 --> 00:02:23,060
she would not betray Tian Wai Tian.

32
00:02:25,340 --> 00:02:27,720
Maybe she didn't betray Tian Wai Tian.

33
00:02:27,720 --> 00:02:29,540
But one thing's for sure now.

34
00:02:29,540 --> 00:02:34,060
She is not who she used to be.

35
00:02:34,060 --> 00:02:35,880
I don't understand.

36
00:02:38,300 --> 00:02:40,640
I don't know what Young Lady is thinking.

37
00:02:41,220 --> 00:02:43,660
She's in Tianqi.

38
00:02:43,660 --> 00:02:46,680
You can head there and ask her personally.

39
00:02:47,540 --> 00:02:52,040
However, something else is more important now.

40
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:55,140
What is it?

41
00:02:56,220 --> 00:02:58,640
I found...

42
00:03:01,100 --> 00:03:03,500
another natural martial artist.

43
00:03:05,700 --> 00:03:08,300
Another natural martial artist?

44
00:03:08,300 --> 00:03:10,380
What is happening?

45
00:03:10,380 --> 00:03:13,940
I didn't see Baili Dongjun, but I saw two other people.

46
00:03:13,940 --> 00:03:16,900
One of them overexerted his inner strength within a short time.

47
00:03:16,900 --> 00:03:19,100
He might have used the Immovable Lord Technique.

48
00:03:19,100 --> 00:03:22,280
- Immovable Lord Technique? 
 - Exactly.

49
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:26,940
When we fought, he forced himself to use his inner strength.

50
00:03:27,700 --> 00:03:30,020
How brave of him.

51
00:03:30,020 --> 00:03:34,420
Those who wish to practice the Immovable Lord Technique must have a robust meridian system.

52
00:03:34,420 --> 00:03:38,940
If one's inner strength is depleted while using it, one's meridian system will be damaged.

53
00:03:38,940 --> 00:03:42,340
To force himself to generate inner strength within a short period of time...

54
00:03:43,260 --> 00:03:46,800
Does he want to be crippled forever?

55
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:49,180
Here comes the interesting part.

56
00:03:49,180 --> 00:03:53,120
I noticed his meridian system is not damaged at all.

57
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:55,740
A natural martial artist.

58
00:03:55,740 --> 00:03:58,140
I thought the same way.

59
00:03:58,140 --> 00:04:01,220
Only a natural martial artist has such a robust meridian system.

60
00:04:01,220 --> 00:04:04,200
Bringing him back would achieve our goal too.

61
00:04:04,200 --> 00:04:07,160
- Where is he? 
 - Prince Jingyu's Mansion.

62
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:09,640
Prince Jingyu's Mansion?

63
00:04:11,320 --> 00:04:15,020
Send a message to our sect and investigate the origin of this person.

64
00:04:15,020 --> 00:04:20,640
Immovable Lord Technique is the signature technique of Nanjue's best martial artist, Rain Demon.

65
00:04:20,640 --> 00:04:25,300
This natural martial artist must have an interesting background.

66
00:04:26,860 --> 00:04:30,260
By the way Yuji, since last night

67
00:04:30,260 --> 00:04:33,640
Twin Lords Wuzuo have been missing.

68
00:04:33,640 --> 00:04:36,280
Did you find any sect's mark?

69
00:04:38,700 --> 00:04:43,180
Normally if they leave Tianqi in advance,

70
00:04:43,180 --> 00:04:47,860
they will inform us by letter or leave marks as they leave.

71
00:04:47,860 --> 00:04:53,500
This seems to suggest that the situation is dire.

72
00:05:00,900 --> 00:05:04,860
He looks just like Brother Yun when he was little.

73
00:05:04,860 --> 00:05:07,920
I wonder how Brother Yun is doing now.

74
00:05:25,020 --> 00:05:26,800
Junior Sister.

75
00:05:28,300 --> 00:05:30,480
The other person is awake.

76
00:05:32,540 --> 00:05:34,400
Thank you for saving me, Miss.

77
00:05:34,400 --> 00:05:38,420
Spare the formalities when you're still injured.

78
00:05:40,540 --> 00:05:43,000
- As for my friend... 
 - Don't worry.

79
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:45,140
He'll be fine as long as I'm here.

80
00:05:45,140 --> 00:05:47,380
Thank you, Miss.

81
00:05:47,380 --> 00:05:50,580
Miss, may I know where we are?

82
00:05:50,580 --> 00:05:52,820
Prince Jingyu's Mansion.

83
00:05:52,820 --> 00:05:55,620
What? Prince Jingyu's Mansion?

84
00:05:55,620 --> 00:05:58,920
- Then you're... 
 - Of course, I'm the future Princess Consort Jingyu.

85
00:05:58,920 --> 00:06:02,420
It's just that I'm not married yet.

86
00:06:02,420 --> 00:06:05,660
- So His Highness saved us? 
 - No, I did.

87
00:06:05,660 --> 00:06:08,700
Prince Jingyu has nothing to do with this.

88
00:06:08,700 --> 00:06:11,580
It just so happened that you fell into my yard.

89
00:06:11,580 --> 00:06:14,960
And I, and this...

90
00:06:17,900 --> 00:06:19,570
Ye Dingzhi.

91
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:22,420
Ye Dingzhi.

92
00:06:22,420 --> 00:06:25,180
It sounds like a heroic name.

93
00:06:26,700 --> 00:06:30,280
Ye Dingzhi caught my eye so I saved you two.

94
00:06:30,280 --> 00:06:32,080
That's all?

95
00:06:32,080 --> 00:06:34,160
Yes.

96
00:06:48,940 --> 00:06:50,700
Master.

97
00:06:50,700 --> 00:06:52,220
Master?

98
00:06:52,220 --> 00:06:54,140
Is he already here?

99
00:06:59,500 --> 00:07:01,300
I guess not.

100
00:07:02,700 --> 00:07:06,180
Dongjun, I don't think Ye Dingzhi is coming.

101
00:07:10,300 --> 00:07:12,020
Impossible.

102
00:07:12,020 --> 00:07:14,440
Let's wait a bit longer. He'll be here for sure.

103
00:07:14,440 --> 00:07:17,820
No. You've been waiting for a day.

104
00:07:17,820 --> 00:07:19,780
Did something bad happen?

105
00:07:19,780 --> 00:07:21,880
Dongjun.

106
00:07:21,880 --> 00:07:25,320
Taking someone as your master is not just about your potential or luck.

107
00:07:25,320 --> 00:07:28,540
Do you know what the most important part is?

108
00:07:28,540 --> 00:07:30,340
It's fate.

109
00:07:30,940 --> 00:07:34,220
It seems like I am fated to take only one disciple today.

110
00:07:35,820 --> 00:07:37,520
No.

111
00:07:37,520 --> 00:07:39,460
I have to go find him.

112
00:08:24,300 --> 00:08:26,760
His Highness seems to be really careless.

113
00:08:26,760 --> 00:08:29,080
He doesn't even come to this huge yard.

114
00:08:29,080 --> 00:08:32,340
There's only his future consort and her senior.

115
00:08:37,940 --> 00:08:40,080
That's so fast!

116
00:08:41,820 --> 00:08:43,340
Mind your word, Sir.

117
00:08:43,340 --> 00:08:48,080
My senior will soon become someone even Prince Jingyu would not want to mess with.

118
00:09:10,780 --> 00:09:12,500
Junior Sister.

119
00:09:14,700 --> 00:09:16,580
Senior, don't worry.

120
00:09:16,580 --> 00:09:18,540
I know what I'm doing.

121
00:09:55,260 --> 00:09:58,820
Being good-looking comes with its own perks.

122
00:09:58,820 --> 00:10:01,380
What do you mean?

123
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:06,720
If you were in his place, you might not have been given this Frostpeak Water.

124
00:10:08,260 --> 00:10:12,680
I look charming, don't I?

125
00:10:17,620 --> 00:10:19,860
Far worse than him.

126
00:10:42,060 --> 00:10:44,040
Water...

127
00:10:45,500 --> 00:10:47,260
Water...

128
00:11:15,500 --> 00:11:20,580
Fairy... Fairy...

129
00:11:29,840 --> 00:11:31,500
It's all right.

130
00:11:53,820 --> 00:11:57,880
Brother Ye, are you awake? You...

131
00:11:59,340 --> 00:12:01,140
Watch out.

132
00:12:03,980 --> 00:12:07,000
Senior, Hero Wang.

133
00:12:10,025 --> 00:12:12,025

134
00:12:17,020 --> 00:12:18,780
This is Luo Qingyang. He's...

135
00:12:18,780 --> 00:12:23,960
He's the head disciple of the Shadow Sect, Luo Qingyang.

136
00:12:24,920 --> 00:12:28,520
Have we met before?

137
00:12:28,520 --> 00:12:32,520
 He is Luo Qingyang. Then she is...

138
00:12:32,520 --> 00:12:35,060
 Brother Yun, over here!

139
00:12:35,060 --> 00:12:36,880
 She is...

140
00:12:37,960 --> 00:12:39,860
 Wenjun.

141
00:12:53,800 --> 00:12:59,780
Why are you gawking? Oh, right. This is our savior, Princess Consort Jingyu.

142
00:12:59,780 --> 00:13:03,820
Don't call me Princess Consort. Prince Jingyu and I aren't married yet.

143
00:13:07,480 --> 00:13:10,900
Hero Wang, how is your injury?

144
00:13:10,900 --> 00:13:16,000
Thanks to your and Brother Luo's timely rescue, there were no internal injuries. I am completely healed now.

145
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:20,460
Well, you're not being chased by those fighters anymore, are you?

146
00:13:20,460 --> 00:13:26,020
No way. His Majesty once gave Mount Wangcheng the Plaque of Integrity.

147
00:13:26,020 --> 00:13:30,060
It proves that we have high integrity and are to be treated as esteemed guests everywhere we go.

148
00:13:30,060 --> 00:13:33,840
That night was nothing but an accident.

149
00:13:33,840 --> 00:13:39,640
If so, why are you still here?

150
00:13:47,840 --> 00:13:51,800
Well, Brother Ye, are you...

151
00:13:55,300 --> 00:13:57,280
I...

152
00:14:52,060 --> 00:14:54,360
You're awake.

153
00:15:00,180 --> 00:15:04,340
Little girl, where am I?

154
00:15:04,340 --> 00:15:08,800
You're at my home. My father brought you back.

155
00:15:08,800 --> 00:15:12,760
I know this is your home. So, who are you?

156
00:15:12,760 --> 00:15:15,300
I am Li Hanyi.

157
00:15:15,300 --> 00:15:17,700
 Li Hanyi?

158
00:15:24,100 --> 00:15:26,200
I see.

159
00:15:27,980 --> 00:15:31,260
You're Mister Li's daughter.

160
00:15:31,260 --> 00:15:35,640
How old is he? His daughter is so young.

161
00:15:41,480 --> 00:15:45,041
Hanyi, our guest is awake?

162
00:15:46,480 --> 00:15:48,360
Mother.

163
00:15:55,920 --> 00:15:57,660
Oh, my.

164
00:15:58,700 --> 00:16:00,700
Oh, my.

165
00:16:00,700 --> 00:16:05,380
Mother, that uncle is very odd. Is something wrong with his head?

166
00:16:05,380 --> 00:16:08,500
He's as annoying as Father.

167
00:16:09,380 --> 00:16:12,680
Mind your words. You can't call him that.

168
00:16:19,960 --> 00:16:22,620
Greetings, Master's Wife.

169
00:16:24,260 --> 00:16:27,700
I am Baili Dongjun. Nice to meet you.

170
00:16:34,960 --> 00:16:39,300
How come I do not know that I have a disciple now?

171
00:16:40,600 --> 00:16:45,380
This is my wife. This is my daughter. This is my house, you fool.

172
00:16:45,380 --> 00:16:47,780
Did you just call her Master's Wife?

173
00:16:47,780 --> 00:16:52,380
I know that by right I am your senior.

174
00:16:52,380 --> 00:16:55,220
And I don't mind you treating me as your master.

175
00:16:55,220 --> 00:17:00,000
How about this? Don't call me Master. Call me Father instead.

176
00:17:00,720 --> 00:17:04,700
Go away! I only had the wrong idea because your daughter's surname is Li.

177
00:17:04,700 --> 00:17:06,820
She took my surname.

178
00:17:07,660 --> 00:17:09,680
May I know your name?

179
00:17:10,380 --> 00:17:13,180
I am Li Xinyue of Sword Heart Tomb.

180
00:17:14,700 --> 00:17:20,700
My uncle told me it's a sword-forging family far superior to Famous Swords Manor.

181
00:17:20,700 --> 00:17:25,880
Not bad, Brother Lei. You are formidable outside, but when you're home, you're a matrilocal husband.

182
00:17:25,880 --> 00:17:27,640
Of course.

183
00:17:31,540 --> 00:17:36,100
T-The Lei Family of Thunderbolt Sect is just as famous in the martial arts world.

184
00:17:36,100 --> 00:17:39,580
D-Don't call me a matrilocal husband. I... I'll kill you.

185
00:17:39,580 --> 00:17:42,060
Then tell me why your daughter didn't take your surname.

186
00:17:42,060 --> 00:17:45,580
I... She... I...

187
00:17:46,340 --> 00:17:52,720
Because Father was expelled from Lei Fortress. His children cannot take Lei as their surname.

188
00:17:52,720 --> 00:17:57,660
I don't want Lei as my surname either. It sounds fierce.

189
00:17:58,560 --> 00:18:04,280
Hanyi, let's go back inside. Let your father talk to this uncle here.

190
00:18:04,280 --> 00:18:05,860
Let's go.

191
00:18:10,420 --> 00:18:15,140
Fine. Now that you're awake, I'll take you to see Master.

192
00:18:15,140 --> 00:18:16,780
Wait.

193
00:18:17,600 --> 00:18:20,760
Where is Ye Dingzhi? Did he come back?

194
00:18:23,540 --> 00:18:25,920
No. I have to find him.

195
00:18:25,920 --> 00:18:28,420
You don't need to find him.

196
00:18:28,420 --> 00:18:30,620
Brother Wang, you're back.

197
00:18:31,860 --> 00:18:35,180
Where is Ye Dingzhi? Did he enter the Academy already?

198
00:18:35,180 --> 00:18:41,920
Well, he is recuperating at the safest place in Tianqi City.

199
00:18:41,920 --> 00:18:47,300
He's accompanied by a ravishing beauty. You don't need to worry about him.

200
00:18:47,300 --> 00:18:49,520
What do you mean?

201
00:18:50,500 --> 00:18:54,860
 If so, why are you still here?

202
00:19:03,020 --> 00:19:04,700
 Fine.

203
