 I...

205
00:19:13,700 --> 00:19:15,980
 I won't leave yet.

206
00:19:17,380 --> 00:19:19,000
 Brother Wang.

207
00:19:19,000 --> 00:19:24,780
 Please tell Dongjun to put effort into learning from Mister Li.

208
00:19:24,780 --> 00:19:26,960
 I'll wait for the day when he becomes famous.

209
00:19:26,960 --> 00:19:28,340
That's all?

210
00:19:28,340 --> 00:19:30,720
- He only said that? 
 - Yes.

211
00:19:32,880 --> 00:19:34,740
Brother Wang.

212
00:19:34,740 --> 00:19:39,620
Who else, other than you, knows that the lady saved you?

213
00:19:39,620 --> 00:19:43,260
Other than us, our mysterious pursuer knows about it too.

214
00:19:43,260 --> 00:19:45,760
Don't tell anyone else, then.

215
00:19:45,760 --> 00:19:49,580
The affairs of the court can be quite complicated.

216
00:19:49,580 --> 00:19:53,620
Since that lady said that her help was something personal,

217
00:19:53,620 --> 00:19:55,860
