♫  With faith that conquers the world with one strike  ♫

258
00:23:18,957 --> 00:23:22,132
Martial Uncle Baili, after you.

259
00:23:23,520 --> 00:23:24,850
Sure.

260
00:23:24,850 --> 00:23:27,517
♫  Breaking through the waves, dancing drunkenly everywhere  ♫

261
00:23:27,517 --> 00:23:30,197
♫  Protecting the people, no matter the cost  ♫

262
00:23:30,197 --> 00:23:35,997
♫  Atop the peak, you and I shall battle all out  ♫

263
00:23:53,277 --> 00:23:55,697
- He actually dodged it. 
 - He actually dodged it.

264
00:23:56,577 --> 00:23:58,757
Curse it!

265
00:23:58,757 --> 00:24:04,337
I managed to prank all his seniors but he dodged it like I did when I was young.

266
00:24:04,337 --> 00:24:06,857
That's not good.

267
00:24:17,980 --> 00:24:20,560
So boring. You're really boring.

268
00:24:20,560 --> 00:24:23,740
It's a solemn ritual, but you're pulling a trick I used to play.

269
00:24:23,740 --> 00:24:25,660
I am the overlord of Qiandong City.

270
00:24:25,660 --> 00:24:28,320
Try something new next time.

271
00:24:29,020 --> 00:24:30,300
All right.

272
00:24:30,300 --> 00:24:33,340
While the opening act leaves much to be desired,

273
00:24:33,340 --> 00:24:38,740
let's get back to business and begin the Academy's apprenticeship ritual.

274
00:24:38,740 --> 00:24:40,480
Baili Dongjun.

275
00:24:41,060 --> 00:24:43,100
Yin Luoxia.

276
00:24:43,100 --> 00:24:45,140
I am Xiao Ruofeng.

277
00:24:45,140 --> 00:24:47,180
I know that already.

278
00:24:47,900 --> 00:24:50,420
I am Mister Li's seventh disciple.

279
00:24:50,420 --> 00:24:55,900
From now on, you may call me Seventh Senior, or Seventh Martial Uncle.

280
00:24:55,900 --> 00:24:59,840
Of course, you can call me Little Senior too.

281
00:25:01,180 --> 00:25:03,040
Senior.

282
00:25:03,040 --> 00:25:04,940
Seventh Martial Uncle.

283
00:25:10,380 --> 00:25:15,020
I'm Mister Li's sixth disciple, Luo Xuan.

284
00:25:16,580 --> 00:25:18,100
Sixth Senior.

285
00:25:18,100 --> 00:25:19,900
Sixth Martial Uncle.

286
00:25:21,580 --> 00:25:23,920
I'm Mister Li's fourth disciple.

287
00:25:23,920 --> 00:25:26,280
- Mo... 
 - Liu Yue.

288
00:25:26,860 --> 00:25:28,740
Xiaohei.

289
00:25:36,020 --> 00:25:37,720
Fifth Martial Uncle.

290
00:25:53,940 --> 00:25:55,520
Master.

291
00:26:04,600 --> 00:26:07,620
It sure is different when one has a disciple already.

292
00:26:07,620 --> 00:26:09,340
Don't you think so?

293
00:26:10,620 --> 00:26:12,100
Get up.

294
00:26:18,740 --> 00:26:20,520
Senior Mochen.

295
00:26:21,180 --> 00:26:23,020
Senior Liu Yue.

296
00:26:27,860 --> 00:26:30,500
Isn't this Young Master Lingyun, Gu Jianmen?

297
00:26:30,500 --> 00:26:35,300
Gu Jianmen is your Third Senior.

298
00:26:36,340 --> 00:26:41,240
And I am Mister Li's second disciple,

299
00:26:41,240 --> 00:26:47,460
also known as Young Master Zhuomo and your Second Senior.

300
00:26:47,460 --> 00:26:49,420
Second Senior?

301
00:26:50,480 --> 00:26:53,340
Lei'er sounds better to my ears.

302
00:26:54,220 --> 00:26:56,860
How rude of you.

303
00:27:03,020 --> 00:27:04,180
Address me properly.

304
00:27:04,180 --> 00:27:07,120
- Quickly. 
 - Fine. Just to make you look good.

305
00:27:07,980 --> 00:27:09,600
Second Senior.

306
00:27:10,940 --> 00:27:12,720
Second Martial Uncle.

307
00:27:13,580 --> 00:27:15,140
Hi, Junior.

308
00:27:15,140 --> 00:27:18,180
Hi, Junior Niece.

309
00:27:21,540 --> 00:27:23,380
Where is First Senior?

310
00:27:27,380 --> 00:27:28,940
He never existed.

311
00:27:28,940 --> 00:27:31,140
When I started here, I was already the second disciple.

312
00:27:31,140 --> 00:27:34,060
I have never seen him. None of them have seen him either.

313
00:27:34,060 --> 00:27:35,860
Master never explained.

314
00:27:35,860 --> 00:27:38,140
How odd.

315
00:27:38,140 --> 00:27:39,280
Exactly.

316
00:27:39,280 --> 00:27:44,420
Master said that the odder a person was, the more likely he'd become a martial genius.

317
00:27:44,420 --> 00:27:46,140
Look at me. I am odd.

318
00:27:46,140 --> 00:27:49,920
Liu Yue is also odd. They are odd. And you...

319
00:27:49,920 --> 00:27:51,700
Are you complimenting me?

320
00:27:51,700 --> 00:27:53,020
Yes.

321
00:27:53,020 --> 00:27:55,020
Master is the oddest of them all.

322
00:27:55,020 --> 00:27:57,820
 Lei'er, you talk too much.

323
00:27:57,820 --> 00:27:59,500
All right.

324
00:27:59,500 --> 00:28:01,140
Junior.

325
00:28:01,740 --> 00:28:03,440
Go.

326
00:28:05,980 --> 00:28:08,460
Must you do this?

327
00:28:14,140 --> 00:28:15,940
You don't need to do this to me.

328
00:28:15,940 --> 00:28:18,960
You're becoming my disciple, not getting married.

329
00:28:18,960 --> 00:28:20,900
Master.

330
00:28:20,900 --> 00:28:25,660
Dongba, from now on, you are my youngest disciple.

331
00:28:30,580 --> 00:28:33,020
Master, please accept my bow.

332
00:28:33,020 --> 00:28:34,600
Wonderful.

333
00:28:36,820 --> 00:28:40,140
Did you just call me "Dongba"?

334
00:28:40,140 --> 00:28:45,140
Lei'er, Jiansan, Liusi, Heiwu, Xuanliu, and Fengqi. You will naturally be Dongba.

335
00:28:45,140 --> 00:28:48,440
Master. You're really so boring.

336
00:28:49,140 --> 00:28:50,860
Yes.

337
00:28:52,300 --> 00:28:57,820
I've lived so long that many things become boring.

338
00:28:57,820 --> 00:29:00,940
Therefore, I must do something to entertain myself.

339
00:29:00,940 --> 00:29:03,260
How long have you lived?

340
00:29:10,580 --> 00:29:12,800
Back then, my slash shook the Heavens.

341
00:29:12,800 --> 00:29:17,000
Immortals descended and told me that I did not belong to the mortal realm,

342
00:29:17,000 --> 00:29:19,600
and that I should live in Heaven.

343
00:29:19,600 --> 00:29:22,900
They wanted to take me with them but I said no.

344
00:29:22,900 --> 00:29:28,200
The Immortals then touched my head and said that they would give me immortality

345
00:29:28,200 --> 00:29:30,600
so that I could experience the mortal life fully.

346
00:29:30,600 --> 00:29:34,800
This scene was witnessed by the Poetry Deity, and a great poem was born.

347
00:29:34,800 --> 00:29:38,980
A divine touch on my head and thus I was given a long life.

348
00:29:39,600 --> 00:29:42,300
Guess how long I have lived?

349
00:29:42,300 --> 00:29:43,900
Is this true?

350
00:29:45,380 --> 00:29:46,980
Of course...

351
00:29:48,060 --> 00:29:49,940
it's fake.

352
00:29:52,000 --> 00:29:53,800
- Why is this disciple so stupid? 
 - This old geezer.

353
00:29:53,800 --> 00:29:56,500
People from the Martial World are cunning.

354
00:29:57,600 --> 00:30:00,500
You know what? I'll take you out one month from now.

355
00:30:00,500 --> 00:30:03,500
I'll show you the worst of the Martial World.

356
00:30:03,500 --> 00:30:05,400
Why one month from now?

357
00:30:05,400 --> 00:30:08,300
Don't you want to drink Qiulubai from Diaolou Tavern?

358
00:30:08,300 --> 00:30:11,800
Qiulubai is only available once per month.

359
00:30:16,000 --> 00:30:19,800
Oh, no. It's all gone for this month.

360
00:30:19,800 --> 00:30:21,800
Worry not. Just wait until next month.

361
00:30:21,800 --> 00:30:25,400
You can drink to your heart's content and then we'll depart.

362
00:30:27,700 --> 00:30:29,000
Oh right. Master.

363
00:30:29,000 --> 00:30:32,000
Someone once hinted at me that I was a natural martial artist.

364
00:30:32,000 --> 00:30:35,000
Wang also told me just now that Ye Dingzhi was a natural martial artist.

365
00:30:35,000 --> 00:30:37,400
What does that mean?

366
00:30:39,620 --> 00:30:47,180
Being a natural martial artist is both a blessing, and a curse.

367
00:30:48,500 --> 00:30:50,000
All right.

368
00:30:50,000 --> 00:30:53,000
That's all for today's questions.

369
00:30:53,000 --> 00:30:55,600
I'm sleepy.

370
00:30:55,600 --> 00:30:57,300
Wait.

371
00:30:59,800 --> 00:31:02,700
What a weird and stubborn old man.

372
00:31:09,020 --> 00:31:10,560
Come on.

373
00:31:11,740 --> 00:31:15,380
Tell me. What nickname did Master give you?

374
00:31:16,400 --> 00:31:20,200
I wonder what he called you. Maybe Bailiba?

375
00:31:20,200 --> 00:31:22,900
But Mo Xiaohei said Master was lazy and he'd only use a two-syllable nickname.

376
00:31:22,900 --> 00:31:26,700
He thinks your nickname is Liba. So, what's your nickname?

377
00:31:30,400 --> 00:31:32,600
Dongba.

378
00:31:39,700 --> 00:31:42,800
Oh, fellow seniors. Master told me that he had lived a long life.

379
00:31:42,800 --> 00:31:44,600
How old is he?

380
00:31:44,600 --> 00:31:46,200
We have no idea either.

381
00:31:46,200 --> 00:31:49,200
Last year, he celebrated his 80th birthday.

382
00:31:49,200 --> 00:31:50,900
This year, he celebrated his 70th birthday.

383
00:31:50,900 --> 00:31:53,800
I guess next year, it'll be his 100th birthday.

384
00:31:53,800 --> 00:31:55,300
That's the way he is.

385
00:31:55,300 --> 00:31:58,400
He makes up things on the spot. Just ignore him.

386
00:31:59,300 --> 00:32:01,500
Dongba.

387
00:32:01,500 --> 00:32:03,400
Lei'er.

388
00:32:03,400 --> 00:32:04,500
- Dongba. 
 - Lei'er.

389
00:32:04,500 --> 00:32:06,600
- Dongba. 
 - Er.

390
00:32:16,740 --> 00:32:18,260
I...

391
00:32:43,800 --> 00:32:48,200
You look like you're having the world's best delicacy.

392
00:32:48,200 --> 00:32:50,000
I took a bite,

393
00:32:50,000 --> 00:32:52,900
but it's just a plate of pickled vegetables so salty it could kill a cow.

394
00:32:52,900 --> 00:32:56,700
And the cheapest liquor sold in the town ahead.

395
00:32:56,700 --> 00:32:59,100
Yet you actually enjoyed them.

396
00:33:00,600 --> 00:33:03,300
If you nearly starved to death once,

397
00:33:03,300 --> 00:33:06,000
you'd be forever grateful for every kind of food in this world.

398
00:33:06,000 --> 00:33:11,200
You were nearly killed by your illness, why aren't you grateful for these herbs?

399
00:33:11,200 --> 00:33:14,900
How could you just sit and watch as your master grinds herbs?

400
00:33:16,400 --> 00:33:21,800
Anyway, I have learned all you have to teach me.

401
00:33:21,800 --> 00:33:24,900
- Based on our agreement, tomorrow— 
 - As soon as the sun rises tomorrow

402
00:33:24,900 --> 00:33:26,900
you will have nothing more to do with herbs.

403
00:33:26,900 --> 00:33:30,300
I remember this. I do.

404
00:33:33,300 --> 00:33:38,080
I might just be the most pathetic master in this world.

405
00:33:39,000 --> 00:33:41,800
You have the talent for medicine.

406
00:33:41,800 --> 00:33:43,400
In a few months

407
00:33:43,400 --> 00:33:47,700
you've mastered what would take an ordinary person years or decades to learn.

408
00:33:47,700 --> 00:33:50,100
Why aren't you interested in it?

409
00:33:54,700 --> 00:33:58,000
How long have you stayed in the valley?

410
00:34:00,500 --> 00:34:03,000
I came to Medicine Valley when I was 12.

411
00:34:03,000 --> 00:34:07,000
I suppose it has been 26 years.

412
00:34:07,000 --> 00:34:08,700
That's so long.

413
00:34:08,700 --> 00:34:10,800
Do you feel lonely?

414
00:34:10,800 --> 00:34:13,500
The valley is secluded. No one comes here.

415
00:34:13,500 --> 00:34:16,400
Even if they do you only see people on the brink of death like me.

416
00:34:16,400 --> 00:34:20,700
I think, since you're great at medicine you should go out.

417
00:34:20,700 --> 00:34:24,300
Some want to make a name for themselves and make big achievements.

418
00:34:24,300 --> 00:34:27,400
Some just want to enjoy peace alone.

419
00:34:27,400 --> 00:34:31,900
How many lives cross over today, and how many lives are born?

420
00:34:31,900 --> 00:34:33,600
It's all destiny.

421
00:34:33,600 --> 00:34:37,500
Even if I go out, how many lives can I save?

422
00:34:37,500 --> 00:34:43,200
If, like you, they stumble upon Medicine Valley, they are fated to see me.

423
00:34:43,200 --> 00:34:47,900
Regardless of their background or motive, I will save them.

424
00:34:49,800 --> 00:34:51,800
So you're happy to live like this forever?

425
00:34:51,800 --> 00:34:54,100
A life without any change?

426
00:34:54,100 --> 00:34:57,800
In your eyes I'm doing the same thing everyday.

427
00:34:57,800 --> 00:35:02,400
But in my eyes every day is different.

428
00:35:02,400 --> 00:35:06,500
In spring, Zhuwang Grass will grow on the cliff.

429
00:35:06,500 --> 00:35:10,100
During the solar term, Jingzhe, night dews can compliment Baiqing Pills.

430
00:35:10,100 --> 00:35:14,100
Horseweeds in Qingming can be made into herb bricks.

431
00:35:14,100 --> 00:35:16,900
How is this doing the same thing?

432
00:35:20,500 --> 00:35:21,900
What's on your mind?

433
00:35:21,900 --> 00:35:24,200
Your friend?

434
00:35:24,200 --> 00:35:25,800
Yes.

435
00:35:25,800 --> 00:35:28,200
I wonder how he's doing in Tianqi City.

436
00:35:28,200 --> 00:35:30,500
Is he as cocky as usual?

437
00:35:31,600 --> 00:35:34,300
 I came all the way to run a tavern here.

438
00:35:34,300 --> 00:35:36,600
 Of course, I have some tricks up my sleeves.

439
00:35:36,600 --> 00:35:38,300
 Run!

440
00:35:39,280 --> 00:35:41,720
 Is he being hunted by someone?

441
00:35:42,420 --> 00:35:46,720
 Is he accompanied by trusted friends?

442
00:36:04,200 --> 00:36:11,900
In fact, one day I'll leave this valley too.

443
00:36:14,100 --> 00:36:19,500
To admire and travel the world outside.

444
00:36:21,000 --> 00:36:22,600
When?

445
00:36:24,260 --> 00:36:29,060
When I find a real heir, your junior.

446
00:36:31,100 --> 00:36:35,300
I'm sorry, then. I will not stay by your side.

447
00:36:37,900 --> 00:36:41,700
I will pulverize the medicine into pills and put them in your luggage.

448
00:36:41,700 --> 00:36:45,500
Take one after lunch every day. There are 100 pills in total.

449
00:36:45,500 --> 00:36:48,600
I also asked for a specific herbal powder from the Mu Family of Qingzhou.

450
00:36:48,600 --> 00:36:56,500
I don't want them to know where I live, so please help me retrieve it.

451
00:36:58,800 --> 00:37:03,500
But Qingzhou is too far.

452
00:37:03,500 --> 00:37:04,900
What Qingzhou?

453
00:37:04,900 --> 00:37:09,500
The Mu Family's best apothecary is Qiulu Apothecary and it's in Tianqi City.

454
00:37:09,500 --> 00:37:12,100
And you're heading to Tianqi City.

455
00:37:13,700 --> 00:37:15,800
Don't you want to go there?

456
00:37:15,800 --> 00:37:17,200
Go, then.

457
00:37:17,200 --> 00:37:20,100
100 pills are enough to keep you alive until next year.

458
00:37:20,100 --> 00:37:22,500
Enjoy your stay in Tianqi City.

459
00:37:22,500 --> 00:37:26,000
But do come back to brush up on your knowledge.

460
00:37:43,800 --> 00:37:46,100
The pills are not ready yet.

461
00:37:46,100 --> 00:37:48,100
No need to be this eager.

462
00:38:05,000 --> 00:38:07,800
Tianqi City, here I come!

463
00:38:30,200 --> 00:38:34,200
This dish is called Caged Bird.

464
00:38:34,200 --> 00:38:38,100
And this one is called Distant World.

465
00:38:38,100 --> 00:38:41,000
Please, Young Master Ye.

466
00:38:46,120 --> 00:38:47,700
Brother Luo is not eating?

467
00:38:47,700 --> 00:38:52,180
My senior trains diligently and he is used to an ascetic diet.

468
00:38:52,180 --> 00:38:54,220
No need to worry about him.

469
00:38:56,320 --> 00:39:01,080
Princess Consort, what are you trying to convey

470
00:39:01,080 --> 00:39:03,860
by making these two dishes for me?

471
00:39:03,860 --> 00:39:06,620
I told you not to call me Princess Consort.

472
00:39:08,180 --> 00:39:11,820
I don't want to be a princess consort.

473
00:39:16,740 --> 00:39:18,160
Sure.

474
00:39:18,820 --> 00:39:24,100
If not, Miss, what do you want to talk about?

475
00:39:25,060 --> 00:39:26,740
Tell me, Young Master Ye.

476
00:39:26,740 --> 00:39:28,900
Why did you stay?

477
00:39:28,900 --> 00:39:32,160
I must repay your favor.

478
00:39:32,160 --> 00:39:34,140
As expected from someone I saved.

479
00:39:34,140 --> 00:39:39,640
When I first saw you, I knew you'd be a grateful and loyal person.

480
00:39:39,640 --> 00:39:44,580
It's not because of my good looks?

481
00:39:45,380 --> 00:39:52,360
In fact, when I was unconscious I could hear what you said.

482
00:39:53,980 --> 00:39:55,740
Stop it.

483
00:39:57,020 --> 00:39:59,800
All right, enough joking.

484
00:40:01,880 --> 00:40:04,100
How do you want me to repay your kindness?

485
00:40:04,100 --> 00:40:08,800
I will do everything I can for you.

486
00:40:09,680 --> 00:40:11,820
It's not that serious.

487
00:40:11,820 --> 00:40:13,620
Can you...

488
00:40:14,940 --> 00:40:17,400
Can you tell me about the world outside?

489
00:40:17,400 --> 00:40:20,620
Once you're done, I'll let you go.

490
00:40:24,500 --> 00:40:28,280
I have been staying here for a long time.

491
00:40:28,280 --> 00:40:33,060
While Senior is here, he doesn't talk a lot.

492
00:40:33,060 --> 00:40:37,120
So I hardly talk to anyone.

493
00:40:38,560 --> 00:40:43,500
Like this dish, Caged Bird, I am caged.

494
00:40:43,500 --> 00:40:48,620
But I long for the world outside.

495
00:40:49,460 --> 00:40:52,500
 She is actually leading an unhappy life.

496
00:41:49,540 --> 00:41:51,100
You...

497
00:41:53,760 --> 00:41:57,280
A leaf fell on your hair.

498
00:41:58,540 --> 00:42:00,560
Oh, a leaf.

499
00:42:05,880 --> 00:42:12,660
My martial prowess isn't the best yet.

500
00:42:12,660 --> 00:42:17,200
My eloquence is not so good.

501
00:42:17,200 --> 00:42:19,880
But when it comes to my travel experience,

502
00:42:19,880 --> 00:42:24,480
you might not be able to find someone as well-traveled as myself in Tianqi City.

503
00:42:25,560 --> 00:42:27,480
Where have you been?

504
00:42:27,480 --> 00:42:30,420
I went to the 32 Buddhist States in the Western Regions.

505
00:42:30,420 --> 00:42:33,060
There's a very interesting city.

506
00:42:33,060 --> 00:42:35,840
It's unoccupied, called Muliang.

507
00:42:35,840 --> 00:42:38,600
When I was 13, I followed my master to Nanjue.

508
00:42:38,600 --> 00:42:40,440
I traveled as I practiced martial arts.

509
00:42:40,440 --> 00:42:43,040
The southernmost place I've been to is Mufeng Sea.

510
00:42:43,040 --> 00:42:48,380
And then I traveled north to the northernmost city in Beiman called Suiye.

511
00:42:49,140 --> 00:42:52,600
I was told that the Beiman people were ruthless.

512
00:42:52,600 --> 00:42:57,520
In a fight the winner can take away the loser's tent and wife.

513
00:42:57,520 --> 00:42:59,320
Until a new challenger emerges.

514
00:42:59,320 --> 00:43:00,560
You're wrong.

515
00:43:00,560 --> 00:43:03,620
The Beiman people are actually very kind.

